{"tid":2377694,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"廢人","createTime":"2021-01-23T22:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T01:20:51.000Z","uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"45b316f65fe5d758992df9d2846ede153692f011","tid":2377694,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:03:05.000Z","msg":"我話我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁多年<br />\n仲未識建構屬於自己嘅安全感<br />\n懷疑以後都係咁<br />\n乜都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n我相信自己係一個有能力、有智慧嘅人<br />\n但只可以係狀態好底下先做到<br />\n一開始insecure <br />\n啲責任感、勤奮、善良就唔見曬<br />\n事後自己好内疚好唔開心<br />\n真係好攰好攰<br />\n唔識點樣搵到呢份安全感<br />\n可能一直都處於擔心無地方住無錢食飯嘅狀態<br />\n其實無人要自己、無人理我<br />\n我都唔知可以點<br />\n想過無數次一走了之<br />\n好想脫離呢個現實<br />\n我唔介意帶走埋所有快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以唔好再咁痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e9ce3ff32067fef1dde1ebaa21c38013debb1f","tid":2377694,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:05:30.000Z","msg":"So tell me to leave <br />\nI&rsquo;ll pack my bags<br />\nGet on the roads<br />\n<br />\nFind someone that gives you<br />\nAll the things I could not now"},{"pid":"b0fd9c8aca785ef4853ac6950161fc0327cbcc61","tid":2377694,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:18:48.000Z","msg":"Can you please end my fucking life"},{"pid":"dd1980b47f9cf252f73ee49477e4bd62872eb892","tid":2377694,"uid":9392,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pGVJujw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpGVJujw.png&h=9aabfb98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f6e8ffc3358375aeaf0c5f0ab633f6f8514bcd0","tid":2377694,"uid":10292,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T22:33:06.000Z","msg":"連以前嘅掙扎都唔再想<br />\n唔想再俾任何人去明白<br />\n慢慢離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gi